The '''armored rat''', also called '''ratidillo''', '''rat monster''' or '''kragget rat''', was a large, hard-plated [[Rodent/Legends|rodent]] native to the lower and bedrock [[Coruscant Underworld/Legends|levels]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. A row of lethal spikes ran down its back and tail, and two large tusks jutted from its mouth. They scavenged for whatever little food they could find. It had a strong, painful bite and was known to bite unwary beings without provocation. There was a soft spot at the back of its neck, just between the head and body carapace. It may have been related to the [[borrat]].

During their stay at his restaurant, members of [[Delta Squad/Legends|Delta]] and [[Omega Squad]]s suspected [[Qibbu]] the Hutt of attempting to substitute armored rat for [[Nerf steak/Legends|nerf steak]].

